Default Traits ~ Razor Boar								CATEGORY:Internal																																																																										ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|TYPE=RazorBoarRaceAbility

Trample				KEY:Trample ~ Razor Boar			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RazorBoarRaceAbility.RaceAbility.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary		DESC:As a standard action during its turn each round, a razor boar can trample opponents at least one size category smaller than itself. This attack deals 2d6+12 points of bludgeoning damage. A trampled opponent can attempt either an attack of opportunity at a -4 penalty or a Reflex save (DC 25) for half damage.																					SOURCEPAGE:p.220
Vorpal Tusks			KEY:Vorpal Tusks ~ Razor Boar			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RazorBoarRaceAbility.RaceAbility.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary		DESC:On a successful critical hit against a creature of up to one size category larger than itself, the razor boar's gore attack severs the opponent's head (if it has one) from its body. Though some creatures, such as golems and undead other than vampires, are not affected by the loss of their heads, most creatures die when their heads are cut off.															SOURCEPAGE:p.220
Fast Healing			KEY:Fast Healing ~ Razor Boar			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RazorBoarRaceAbility.RaceAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:A razor boar regains lost hit points at the rate of 10 per round. Fast healing does not restore hit points lost from starvation, thirst, or suffocation, and it does not allow the razor boar to regrow or reattach lost body parts.																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.221
Scent					KEY:Scent ~ Razor Boar				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RazorBoarRaceAbility.RaceAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:A razor boar can detect approaching enemies, sniff out hidden foes, and track by sense of smell.																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.221

